                            <li class="tab active"><a href="#tab02">개인정보처리방침</a></li>
                            <li class="tab"><a href="#tab03">저작권 정책</a></li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="tabConts">
                            <div class="tabPanel" id="tab01">
                                첫번째 탭 내용
                            </div>
